    "updated_at": "2015-09-23T19:06:05Z",
    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "Thank you for the hints, I finally was able to update my custom.js. Here is my final version, if anyone cares. OSX 10.10.5, IPython 4.0.0:\n\n``` js\nrequire([\n    'base/js/namespace',\n    'base/js/events',\n], function (IPython, events) {\n\n    function to(mode) {\n        function to_mode(c) { \n            return c.code_mirror.setOption('keyMap', mode);\n        };\n        IPython.notebook.get_cells().map(to_mode);\n        require(\"notebook/js/cell\").Cell.options_default.cm_config.keyMap = mode;\n    };\n\n    events.on('notebook_loaded.Notebook', function () {\n        require([\"codemirror/keymap/emacs\"], function () {\n            to('emacs')\n            console.log('emacs.js loaded')\n        });\n    });\n});\n```\n"
